Package: Pepi
Type: Package
Title: Pepi - Bayesian method for quantifying plasticity from genomics data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2023-12-5
Author: Riccardo Bergamin
Maintainer: Riccardo Bergamin <rbergamin@units.it>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Riccardo", "Bergamin", "rbergamin@units.it", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Giulio", "Caravagna", "gcaravagn@gmail.com", role = c("ctb"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4240-3265")),
    person("Clara", "Canavese", "arnold@sissa.com", role = c("ctb"))
